AI Model Details:
-> linear regression model
-> inputs -> outputs
-> will train offline
-> will export as .pkl
-> will be created using Python: pandas, scikit-learn, and pickle to save (see above)

Backend:
-> Flask will be the easiest to intergrate with the model and I have past experience with it so it will be a good refresher
-> Flask will have my routes and stuff 